Rating: 3
I made a vegetarian meal out this instead of a side dish by adding pine nuts, walnuts, mozarella cheese, broccoli, and asparagus. It was delicious, and not too difficult to make. I used less butter (only 2 tbsp)than called for for health purposes, and substituted olive oil instead when sauteing the onions and mushrooms. Only comment is that I had to bake the casserole for 75 minutes (not the 25 listed in the recipe) to get the barley to reconstitute.